transcript:
Customer: Aapne jis vyakti ko call kiya hai, vah anya call par vyast hai. Kripya pratiksha karein ya kuch samay pashchat prayas karein. The person you have called is speaking to someone else. You can wait or call again later.
Aapne jis vyakti ko call kiya hai, vah anya call par vyast hai. Kripya pratiksha karein ya kuch samay pashchat prayas karein.
Hello
Executive: Hello
Customer: Haanji madam.
Executive: Hi sir, good afternoon.
Customer: Good afternoon ji.
Executive: Sir, main Ayushi baat kar rahi thi IndiaMART se account manager sir. Giganext Impex se baat kar rahe hain aap?
Customer: Haanji, main Giganext Impex se baat kar raha hun.
Executive: Okay sir, aapka concern aaya tha IndiaMART ke platform mein aapne call kiya tha sir. Concern jaan sakti hun kya pareshani hai abhi?
Customer: Nahi.
Executive: Mera koi concern nahi hai.
Executive: Sir call aaya tha hamare customer care ke number se. Abhi aayi thi morning mein actually main utha nahi payi hun to mere pass call
Customer: Maine to nahi kiya hoga.
Executive: Ji to primary jo number hai usme bhi aate hain sir 946 wala jo number hai starting mein. Wo aapke pass hai kisi aur ke pass hai wo number?
Customer: 926 to nahi hai mera to 98134 hai.
Executive: Nahi nahi jo start primary number hai 946 ending with.
Customer: 946
Executive: Haan last mein.
Customer: Last mein Subhash ji hai ek hamare na.
Executive: Haan haan haan Subhash naam unhi ka hai sir. Haan to basically unhi unhi usi number se aaya tha call hamare pass.
Customer: Haanji.
Executive: Haan to abhi us number pe bhi pick nahi ho raha tha busy ho raha tha isliye main call kiya tha second.
Customer: Wahi handle kar rahe hain aap unhi call kar lijiye.
Executive: Accha accha thik hai thik hai main unhi ko connect kar leti hun unse. Thik hai baki sir isliye jo account manager hai sir main hi hun IndiaMART ke platform pe. To aapko main ek bar aapko bhi whatsapp kar dungi aap mera number save kar lijiyega koi bhi issue hota hai aap mere pass directly connect kar lijiyega. Baki main ek bar unse ek bar coordinate kar leti hun kya issue hai. Thik hai?
Customer: Okay sir okay.
Executive: Thank you sir.
Customer: Okay bhai.
summary:
Concerns:

- Customer stated he had no concerns.



Resolution:

- Executive confirmed call was from customer care.

- Executive offered direct contact for future issues.



Next Steps: 

- Executive will coordinate with Subhash regarding the issue.



Alert (If Any):

None

@@@Sentiment:

- Neutral -> Neutral



@@@Key Topics:
